Welcome to TextWorld! First of all, you could, like, retrieve the key from the floor of the cellar. Once you have taken the key, unlock the safe. Then, open the safe. And then, recover the latchkey from the safe. After that, assure that the locker is locked with the latchkey. Once that's all handled, you can stop!

-= Cellar =-
You arrive in a cellar. A normal one. You decide to start listing off everything you see in the room, as if you were in a text adventure.

You can see a closed locker. What's that over there? It looks like it's a safe. You can make out a box.

There is a closed portal leading west. There is an unguarded exit to the south.

There is a key and a passkey on the floor.

>                                                                                                                                -= Cellar =-0/1

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]take key from floor[command]

You can't see any such thing.

>                                                                                                                                -= Cellar =-0/1

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]take key[command]

You pick up the key from the ground.



>                                                                                                                                -= Cellar =-0/2

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]unlock safe with key[command]

You unlock the safe.


>                                                                                                                                -= Cellar =-0/3

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]open safe[command]

You open the safe, revealing a latchkey.


>                                                                                                                                -= Cellar =-0/4

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]take latchkey from safe[command]

You take the latchkey from the safe.


>                                                                                                                                -= Cellar =-0/5

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]lock locker with latchkey[command]

Get ready to pick stuff up and put it in places, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First stop, go to the south. And then, head east. With that over with, make an effort to go north. With that accomplished, ensure that the type D locker is open. Then, take the keyboard from the type D locker. That's it!

-= Spare Room =-
This might come as a shock to you, but you've just walked into a spare room. You can barely contain your excitement.

You can make out a closed usual looking crate close by. You can make out a rack. However, the rack, like an empty rack, has nothing on it.

There is an exit to the east. Don't worry, it is unblocked. You don't like doors? Why not try going south, that entranceway is unguarded.

>                                                                                                                                -= Spare Room =-0/1

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]go south[command]

-= Dish-Pit =-
You're not going to believe this, but you've just entered a dish-pit.



You don't like doors? Why not try going east, that entranceway is unguarded. You need an unguarded exit? You should try going north.

There is a glass and a fly larva on the floor.


>                                                                                                                                -= Dish-Pit =-0/2

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]go east[command]

-= Cookhouse =-
You arrive in a cookhouse. A typical one.



There is an unblocked exit to the north. You need an unblocked exit? You should try going west.


>                                                                                                                                -= Cookhouse =-0/3

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]go north[command]

-= Studio =-
You are in a studio. A standard kind of place. You begin looking for stuff.

You can see a closed type D locker.

There is an exit to the north. Don't worry, it is unblocked. There is an unguarded exit to the south. You need an unblocked exit? You should try going west.


>                                                                                                                                -= Studio =-0/4

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]open type D locker[command]

You open the type D locker, revealing a keyboard.


>                                                                                                                                -= Studio =-0/5

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]take keyboard from type D locker[command]

Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to pick up the key from the box. Then, check that the hatch is unlocked with the key. Then, assure that the hatch is wide open. And then, take a trip east. And then, pick up the laptop from the bench. That's it!

-= Kitchen =-
You've just sauntered into a kitchen. You can barely contain your excitement.

You see a box. The box contains a key and a spork. Now that's what I call TextWorld!

There is a closed hatch leading east. You need an unblocked exit? You should try going south.

There is a banana on the floor.

>                                                                                                                                -= Kitchen =-0/1

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]take key from box[command]

You take the key from the box.


>                                                                                                                                -= Kitchen =-0/2

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]unlock hatch with key[command]

You unlock hatch.


>                                                                                                                                -= Kitchen =-0/3

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]open hatch[command]

You open hatch.


>                                                                                                                                -= Kitchen =-0/4

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]go east[command]

-= Bedchamber =-
You arrive in a bedchamber. A typical kind of place.

You scan the room, seeing a bench. The bench is ordinary. On the bench you see a laptop. Wow! Just like in the movies!

There is a closed passageway leading south. There is an open hatch leading west.


>                                                                                                                                -= Bedchamber =-0/5

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]take laptop from bench[command]

Then, retrieve the fresh laundry scented key from the locker. After that, attempt to head east. After that, unlock the fresh laundry scented chest. Alright, thanks!

-= Laundromat =-

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.

You can make out a drawer. You can make out a bench. Make a note of this, you might have to put stuff on or in it later on. The bench appears to be empty.

There is an open door leading north. There is an unguarded exit to the south.


>                                                                                                                                -= Shower =-0/2

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]go north[command]

-= Basement =-
You arrive in a basement. A standard kind of place. Let's see what's in here.

If you haven't noticed it already, there seems to be something there by the wall, it's a locker. The locker contains a fresh laundry scented key.

There is an open gate leading east. There is an open door leading south.

There is a keycard on the floor.


>                                                                                                                                -= Basement =-0/3

There is an open gate leading west. There is an unblocked exit to the east.


>                                                                                                                                -= Bedroom =-0/5

 What will you do next? Give me the next command.
[command]unlock fresh laundry scented chest with fresh laundry scented key[command]
